com.hygenics.crawler

Class GetIndividualPages

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.hygenics.crawler.GetIndividualPages

  • public class GetIndividualPages
extends Object
    The purpose of this code is to Get Individual Pages. This page uses the getDAOTemplate. The class works a little differently then the get pages class. It gets individual urls and then runs a loop where specified. The basic object for the pull list is, however, saved. The individual pull nodes can still be discarded.
    Author:
    asevans
